Package yizhong.ding.mavendependencydownloader

package yizhong.ding.mavendependencydownloader
  • Class
    Description
    Artifact
    The Artifact class represents the logical artifact coordinates of maven artifact.
    ArtifactDownloader
    Plays the role of downloading JAR files by using a http based fetcher.
    ArtifactResolveException
    Custom exception that can be thrown if anything goes wrong during artifact resolving.
    DependencyParser
    Plays the role of parsing a list of (direct) dependency of a given Artifact.
    DependencyResolver
    This plays the role of resolving the dependencies of an input artifact and downloads them on a given directory.
    FileWriter
    Plays the role of writing JAR files at the given directory.
    Util
    Util class providing the common methods and URL/Path configurations for the project.
